fields.name: Pokemon Collab Chocolate Cookies - Pack of 16
fields.description: Discover 16 unique Pokémon designs while enjoying America's favorite sandwich cookie with these limited-edition OREO Chocolate Sandwich Cookies. Serve these Pokémon themed OREO cookies as after school snacks or take some with you for delicious office snacks. These snack cookies are also great for parties or mixing into your favorite desserts. There are 16 Pokémon themed OREO cookies to discover. But be aware, some Pokémon are harder to find than others. With a random assortment of Pokémon designs in every package, each package is a chance to find all 16, including one super rare Mythical Pokémon. The resealable container with easy-pull tab keeps these chocolate cookies fresh, and is perfect for snacking, sharing, or traveling throughout your search.
